OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,FThe A76 through Sanquhar has been
OL,8,Fclosed since 1st June to allow repair
OL,9,Fwork on the historic Tollbooth Museum
OL,10,Fto be carried out.
OL,12,FThe road is the main route between
OL,13,FDumfries and Kilmarnock, and the local
OL,14,Fauthority said they had to shut the
OL,15,Froad entirely in order for the work to
OL,16,Fbe done safely.
OL,18,FResidents and businesses have been
OL,19,Fliving with a 50-mile diversion to get
OL,20,Fin and out of town for the past 6
OL,21,Fweeks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
