FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,FSome traders say it's has had a
OL,8,Fnegative impact on trade and that
OL,9,Fthey're looking forward to the road
OL,10,Freopening later today.
OL,12,FNewsagent Charles Brown says its cost
OL,13,Fhim 20% of his business.
OL,15,F"It's been quite stressful, over the
OL,16,Flast 6 weeks we've lost maybe 3 or 4
OL,17,Fthousand pounds.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,F"There's a lot of my customers that I
OL,8,Fknow that just travel to Kirkconnel
OL,9,Fand stop up there, I'm hoping they
OL,10,Fdon't continue doing that. I'm hoping
OL,11,Fthat they revert back to stopping in
OL,12,FSanquhar, but there's no guarantee
OL,13,Fthat's going to happen."
OL,15,FMany residents also report HGVs
OL,16,Fcausing issues ignoring the diversion
OL,17,Froutes and attempting to navigate
OL,18,Fnarrow and unsuitable parts of the
OL,19,Froad.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
