OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,FOne resident even had an HGV hit his
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,FThe traffic restrictions are set to be
OL,11,Fremoved by 6pm this evening (Friday)
OL,12,Fas Dumfries and Galloway Council say
OL,13,Fthe conservation of the tollbooth
OL,14,Fstonework is now almost complete.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
