PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,F"We recognise the impact the A76
OL,8,Frestrictions have had on residents,
OL,9,Fbusinesses, visitors and road users,
OL,10,Fand we would like to thank everyone
OL,11,Ffor their patience and understanding
OL,12,Fthroughout the works," a council
OL,13,Fspokesperson said.
OL,15,F"The feedback from local businesses is
OL,16,Funderstood and appreciated.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
