OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783703991
OL,3,CA76 through Sanquhar set to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing 'devastating' 50 mile
OL,5,Cdiversion
OL,7,F"The conservation works at Sanquhar
OL,8,FTolbooth are now nearing completion,
OL,9,Fwith all traffic restrictions
OL,10,Fscheduled to be removed by 6pm on
OL,11,FFriday 10 July, when the A76 will
OL,12,Ffully reopen to traffic on schedule.
OL,14,F"These essential repairs have helped
OL,15,Fprotect and preserve the Grade A
OL,16,FListed Tolbooth, one of Sanquhar's
OL,17,Fmost significant historic buildings,
OL,18,Fwhile addressing important public
OL,19,Fsafety requirements.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
